description: Home made Belgian waffles with sweet or savory toppings. From across the pond they have brought you two types of waffles: the Brussels, light and crispy and the Liège, made from a dough with pearls of sugar. Perfect for dinner, desserts, or snacks. Example of waffles: Bouc : Brussels waffle, goat cheese, apples, walnuts, honey, thyme.Fraises au chocolat : Your choice of waffle, strawberries, whipped cream, hot Belgian chocolate fudge.
name: Belgian Waffle Crafters
